snippet.textDisplay:
In my opinion, this is one of the stablest Stray Kids live performances. You can clearly hear their live vocals and the choreography isn't as hard as Miroh and Victory Song (so the members can sing/rap with stable voices), but still has the intensity. The vocal line can still hit the high notes and the rap line can still rap their parts powerfully. This Boxer stage is one of their best stages so far. 
Also can we just appreciate 0:33 Jeongin and 1:49 Woojin's low voices, 1:57 Seungmin's note change, 2:02 Felix's kick and 2:18 Minho growling because damn this whole performance snapped.
